{"tid":473951,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"表妹成日唔返學又話心理有問題，點開解佢好。。","createTime":"2017-11-19T16:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T01:37:13.000Z","uid":139763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"547ffcdbc9dd83b529dbcc07d07bd239ba31a88f","tid":473951,"uid":139763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:45:11.000Z","msg":"佢無返學一星期<br />\n會講大話自己打電話番學校請假<br />\n佢媽咪都無佢符<br />\n但頭先同佢食飯佢講野好正常<br />\n我同佢講我啲事佢仲開解到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢同佢媽講自己心理有問題<br />\n就係唔知心理有咩問題<br />\n應該點做好？<br />\n係咪佢純粹唔想返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a94d570d60296088b250583db53af1ff10b2b68","tid":473951,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:46:16.000Z","msg":"介紹俾我<br />\n我幫你開解下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772ca023feb64d98e97d1a953d2fcefc12836775","tid":473951,"uid":139763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:47:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>介紹俾我<br />\n我幫你開解下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 認真？"},{"pid":"f520f0fed7e6a467dcec60ac78ec781fd40587c7","tid":473951,"uid":143686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:49:40.000Z","msg":"佢係咪學校比人恰？定係學校太大壓力？唔番學佢係做啲乜野？出街定係屋企"},{"pid":"42da4e5b6c508f1a1b8367c0459b1b3bcd5f9e48","tid":473951,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:49:58.000Z","msg":"唔想返學姐"},{"pid":"1d542e177c05010ce9884e8f55fac0d70c272128","tid":473951,"uid":41315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:52:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>介紹俾我<br />\n我幫你開解下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 認真？</blockquote><br />\n認真就慢慢同佢傾下計<br />\n了解左佢心事先<br />\n之後先一步一步去同佢一齊探討下之後點 ? <br />\n有乜打算 ? 又或者有無啲咩興趣想去做呢類先會比較好<br />\n<br />\n等佢肯真係放開個心同你傾<br />\n先慢慢引導佢其實逃避都唔係一個解決辦法<br />\n只會進一步拖延佢既理想目標<br />\n<br />\n無理想既要同佢再探討下<br />\n不過大多數香港學生都無<br />\n填鴨教育係教過我地點樣去思考<br />\n<br />\n介紹小表妹就免了<br />\n因為你好難無啦啦介紹一個陌生人同佢探討人生<br />\n如果係靚既就再幫你諗下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46fbfc98b082f789b15adbb9a86545ec123e423a","tid":473951,"uid":139763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:52:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢係咪學校比人恰？定係學校太大壓力？唔番學佢係做啲乜野？出街定係屋企</blockquote><br />\n審犯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我唔知啊 頭先搭車我媽叫我開解佢 我都係從我媽口中先知佢無返學一星期 表妹無同我提過佢返學啲野"},{"pid":"beac9896e9a0995b4e4bb7ed1165f1b09db46e31","tid":473951,"uid":143686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:53:10.000Z","msg":"school bullying -&gt; depression-&gt; 0 motivation -&gt; kids skip school / staying home from school"},{"pid":"487a1677d4917046ec90e6f8226da4aaa2800bcd","tid":473951,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢係咪學校比人恰？定係學校太大壓力？唔番學佢係做啲乜野？出街定係屋企</blockquote><br />\n呢個我都忘記左<br />\n的確都有咁既可能性<br />\n<br />\n但呢樣野更加難問到出黎<br />\n自尊問題更難一個層次<br />\n<br />\n加油樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d094f3965a4c53abc2255f704b481ca08328bbfe","tid":473951,"uid":139763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:54:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔想返學姐</blockquote><br />\n咁簡單？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db7775c0687a89fc125c12351f0848f25e1523d","tid":473951,"uid":143686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:54:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢係咪學校比人恰？定係學校太大壓力？唔番學佢係做啲乜野？出街定係屋企</blockquote><br />\n審犯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我唔知啊 頭先搭車我媽叫我開解佢 我都係從我媽口中先知佢無返學一星期 表妹無同我提過佢返學啲野</blockquote><br />\n直接同我講咪得洗鬼開post"},{"pid":"8b89c40a0774f01eb2707a93fa7af59be73094c8","tid":473951,"uid":139763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:56:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>介紹俾我<br />\n我幫你開解下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 認真？</blockquote><br />\n認真就慢慢同佢傾下計<br />\n了解左佢心事先<br />\n之後先一步一步去同佢一齊探討下之後點 ? <br />\n有乜打算 ? 又或者有無啲咩興趣想去做呢類先會比較好<br />\n<br />\n等佢肯真係放開個心同你傾<br />\n先慢慢引導佢其實逃避都唔係一個解決辦法<br />\n只會進一步拖延佢既理想目標<br />\n<br />\n無理想既要同佢再探討下<br />\n不過大多數香港學生都無<br />\n填鴨教育係教過我地點樣去思考<br />\n<br />\n介紹小表妹就免了<br />\n因為你好難無啦啦介紹一個陌生人同佢探討人生<br />\n如果係靚既就再幫你諗下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好 聽日搵佢傾下<br />\n頭先問佢聽日係咪返學<br />\n佢竟然答我：應該係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近嗰句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 猥瑣啊你"},{"pid":"1412ddef08f3696b8325e3226faa855eb4aa7da2","tid":473951,"uid":139763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>介紹俾我<br />\n我幫你開解下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj