faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 認真？</blockquote><br />\n認真就慢慢同佢傾下計<br />\n了解左佢心事先<br />\n之後先一步一步去同佢一齊探討下之後點 ? <br />\n有乜打算 ? 又或者有無啲咩興趣想去做呢類先會比較好<br />\n<br />\n等佢肯真係放開個心同你傾<br />\n先慢慢引導佢其實逃避都唔係一個解決辦法<br />\n只會進一步拖延佢既理想目標<br />\n<br />\n無理想既要同佢再探討下<br />\n不過大多數香港學生都無<br />\n填鴨教育係教過我地點樣去思考<br />\n<br />\n介紹小表妹就免了<br />\n因為你好難無啦啦介紹一個陌生人同佢探討人生<br />\n如果係靚既就再幫你諗下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好 聽日搵佢傾下<br />\n頭先問佢聽日係咪返學<br />\n佢竟然答我：應該係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後嗰句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 猥瑣啊你</blockquote></blockquote><br />\ncap低左send左俾佢女友 佢等收皮"},{"pid":"b653dc60267ca64f221e6456e335b601f2c65c95","tid":473951,"uid":139814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:59:29.000Z","msg":"俾人欺凌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3420e05b69d482ac14c29383341d8f371e58287c","tid":473951,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:00:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>介紹俾我<br />\n我幫你開解下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 認真？</blockquote><br />\n認真就慢慢同佢傾下計<br />\n了解左佢心事先<br />\n之後先一步一步去同佢一齊探討下之後點 ? <br />\n有乜打算 ? 又或者有無啲咩興趣想去做呢類先會比較好<br />\n<br />\n等佢肯真係放開個心同你傾<br />\n先慢慢引導佢其實逃避都唔係一個解決辦法<br />\n只會進一步拖延佢既理想目標<br />\n<br />\n無理想既要同佢再探討下<br />\n不過大多數香港學生都無<br />\n填鴨教育係教過我地點樣去思考<br />\n<br />\n介紹小表妹就免了<br />\n因為你好難無啦啦介紹一個陌生人同佢探討人生<br />\n如果係靚既就再幫你諗下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好 聽日搵佢傾下<br />\n頭先問佢聽日係咪返學<br />\n佢竟然答我：應該係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近嗰句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 猥瑣啊你</blockquote><br />\n你如果同佢傾得埋既就傾多啲啦<br />\n俾多啲耐性去留意下佢內心既感受<br />\n感受自係最真實, 同埋最會感覺到係被關心<br />\n<br />\n小表妹果句就講笑姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過如果真係需要既<br />\n都可以嘗試下<br />\n我自己都有讀過輔導<br />\n女友都係社工<br />\n如果真係約出黎可以用玩 boardgame 之類藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但就要視乎返你同佢相熟程度而定啦<br />\n同埋住得遠就可能無緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f956950f7168660482b10e7660a037f8566012","tid":473951,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:00:12.000Z","msg":"令佢享受下性愛既歡愉<br />\n之後再慢慢勸下"},{"pid":"9e691ae2b09e3ac91fc5abbdf216d512ea6afd27","tid":473951,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T17:00:42